org.hibernate.ogm.datastore.spi

Class Association

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.hibernate.ogm.datastore.spi.Association

  • public class Association
extends Object
    Represents an Association (think of it as a set of rows) A Association accepts a AssociationShapshot which is a read-only state of the association at creation time. An association collects changes applied to it. These changes are represented by a list of AssociationOperation. It is intended that GridDialects retrieve to these actions and reproduce them to the datastore. The list of changes is computed based off the snapshot.
    Author:
    Emmanuel Bernard
